description:
The Kitchen - Season 2, Episode 13




Summer Party

Special guest Daniel Radcliffe stops by The Kitchen for our Summer Party Show, and plays our first game of Build-A-Burger! The gang has tips and recipes for summer party entertaining, including Katie's incredible grilled Lo Country Shrimp Boil. Design guru Sabrina Soto gussies up the patio and shares DIY projects to make your next outdoor party a hit. Plus, GZ taps into a refreshing Watermelon Cosmo that'll be the hit of your next summer bash.




Original Air Date: 12-Jul-2014
